Light-weight, (mostly) desktop-agnostic programs.

#### Graphical applications

- Archiver: Xarchiver
- Audio player: Audacious
- Calculator: Galculator
- Notepad: Leafpad (Mousepad changed to GTK-3 :( )
- Image viewer: Gpicview 
- Screenshot:  
- Torrent handler:  
- File Manager: PCManFM (of course)
- Terminal: any actually (urxvt, xterm, lxterminal)
- Panel: Tint2 or LxPanel
- Window manager: Openbox
- Appearance changer: LXappearance

